{"tid":175942,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[絲打入]有無絲打唔識用棉條","createTime":"2017-03-28T00:10:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-29T00:22:38.000Z","uid":28834,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2f9f98266036b61e60dc8ca09b2b94db27d0d3d8","tid":175942,"uid":28834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T00:10:32.000Z","msg":"話說同男朋友去旅行諗住用棉條方面d<br />\n點知曬左2支都唔識用 <br />\n<br />\n男朋友同我一齊研究 佢識用我都唔識<br />\n咁每次出門前佢都幫我整好<br />\n<br />\n點知尋日肚痛 去完廁所掉左條棉條之後塞唔番入去<br />\n<br />\n嗚嗚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1785e0d903b8736c2a3b5f78b1b706f990e2f217","tid":175942,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T00:11:20.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"38830bd76662dfb0e715611d64106ac0f41e1ade","tid":175942,"uid":28834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T00:12:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>垃圾</blockquote><br />\n我真係覺得好難用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7503fcaacb5a249290f0d29c823d73589cea069f","tid":175942,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T00:12:57.000Z","msg":"肚痛就冇咗條綿條 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2de387806db8894421afe26aa898ba1977f610a0","tid":175942,"uid":25899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T00:16:19.000Z","msg":"條棉條塞錯落屎眼？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"753c68b1ae2a4cccc220d30f8e592e53aa155a67","tid":175942,"uid":28834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T00:18:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>肚痛就冇咗條綿條 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n痾完屎廢事污糟就諗住一次過換乾淨"},{"pid":"31d0998bbc47104f26eb42c406427188908e545e","tid":175942,"uid":61560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T00:22:18.000Z","msg":"絲打用導管定指入嗰隻？<br />\n新手用導管會易啲(我覺得紙導管&gt;膠導管)<br />\n睇返說明書推到舊嘢得條線喺出面，再好似打針咁推埋入去再抆返導管出黎就得<br />\n姿勢：試下一隻腳抬高踩上廁板慢慢推入去<br />\n最緊要放鬆唔好急同唔好直插入去，要向尾龍骨方向推<br />\n<br />\n利申用左導管式兩年幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7284a72a37f4939d58829fa03024aab7e14747cc","tid":175942,"uid":28834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T00:30:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>絲打用導管定指入嗰隻？<br />\n新手用導管會易啲(我覺得紙導管&gt;膠導管)<br />\n睇返說明書推到舊嘢得條線喺出面，再好似打針咁推埋入去再抆返導管出黎就得<br />\n姿勢：試下一隻腳抬高踩上廁板慢慢推入去<br />\n最緊要放鬆唔好急同唔好直插入去，要向尾龍骨方向推<br />\n<br />\n利申用左導管式兩年幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我果隻係膠<br />\n我初初直頭唔知要塞支膠入去<br />\n到後來塞入去果陣又覺得痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我係日本買 都唔知張說明書寫乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔該絲打 我下次試"},{"pid":"ceace957658b2a9b08f415b083a7e994e8aec2bb","tid":175942,"uid":61560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T00:39:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>絲打用導管定指入嗰隻？<br />\n新手用導管會易啲(我覺得紙導管&gt;膠導管)<br />\n睇返說明書推到舊嘢得條線喺出面，再好似打針咁推埋入去再抆返導管出黎就得<br />\n姿勢：試下一隻腳抬高踩上廁板慢慢推入去<br />\n最緊要放鬆唔好急同唔好直插入去，要向尾龍骨方向推<br />\n<br />\n利申用左導管式兩年幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我果隻係膠<br />\n我初初直頭唔知要塞支膠入去<br />\n到後來塞入去果陣又覺得痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我係日本買 都唔知張說明書寫乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔該絲打 我下次試</blockquote><br />\n上網搵下點用先<br />\n抬腿唔得可以試下踎住/坐喺度mak腳，搵個啱自己嘅姿勢，一路慢慢深呼吸<br />\nm血會有潤滑作用，放入去可能會有啲唔舒服，但痛嘅話就係唔夠放鬆/錯角度/錯位<br />\n一次生兩次熟 熟左就返唔到轉頭用m巾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59242ff3e19958574265412d2dcd1f130ffee99e","tid":175942,"uid":58121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T00:47:51.000Z","msg":"好右問下 咩係棉條？<br />\n利申：巴"},{"pid":"85e07426fc48342024329d6d4de44104529dee1e","tid":175942,"uid":6811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T01:04:55.000Z","msg":"屌 我個陣試過幾條都入唔到，最後用返m巾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18665332dc75e6c5ee9d749ed16de522c3008de3","tid":175942,"uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T01:25:57.000Z","msg":"hi 熱褲"},{"pid":"18e74e8725f998d88eabff5ce3e8b1a34941233a","tid":175942,"uid":82940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T01:31:50.000Z","msg":"處女用唔用得其實"},{"pid":"9503123e021b7438396feadbbb835ac56792eb0e","tid":175942,"uid":31998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T01:32:24.000Z","msg":"用液體m巾都幾好呀，可以唔洗咁快換"},{"pid":"44c899020ce1f851c717e75572aa182517567324","tid":175942,"uid":6156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T01:33:30.000Z","msg":"用過一次 好難放入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1909b534ef3a237923d32f692f84c9797fbe7c8e","tid":175942,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T01:38:28.000Z","msg":"用我條撚塞住先啦"},{"pid":"14489e7e6c93074650189a449ce92df609a076c4","tid":175942,"uid":71411,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T01:44:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用我條撚塞住先啦</blockquote><br />\nGood，呢位同學好有創意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d075b8c2f8b01f6e9755ad05e31a578d4c1f7ce6","tid":175942,"uid":28834,"like":0,"dislike":0,